WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.152
Welcome to the RestoreAssist Setup Wizard.

00:04.152 --> 00:08.600
This 5-step process activates your workspace.

00:08.600 --> 00:11.071
Step 1: Business Profile.

00:11.071 --> 00:17.199
Confirm your business name, ABN, and upload your company logo.

00:17.199 --> 00:19.275
Step 2: AI Hydration.

00:19.275 --> 00:27.275
Industry defaults are auto-loaded — S500 water damage standards, WHS checklists, and report templates.

00:27.275 --> 00:29.351
Step 3: Integrations.

00:29.351 --> 00:37.351
Connect your accounting software — Xero, MYOB, QuickBooks — and job management tools like ServiceM8.

00:37.351 --> 00:39.427
Step 4: Health Check.

00:39.427 --> 00:47.427
We verify 12 capabilities including email, storage, AI models, and compliance engines.

00:47.427 --> 00:49.427
Step 5: Activate.

00:49.427 --> 00:53.084
One tap and your workspace goes live.

00:53.084 --> 00:55.852
Your dashboard is now ready.